Monster.contributionDescription:
Monster will be providing free Monster energy drinks to all participants around dinner time on Saturday Jan 30 2021. 
 
 Make sure to get yours while they last!

Metro Transit.contributionDescription: One thing MinneHack always tries to provide to it's participants is travel reimbursement. Metro Transit has made that a little easier for us by providing all hackers the option of taking one of their various transit lines to and from MinneHack for free!

Sticker Mule.contributionDescription: Hackers love stickers, and Stickermule is making it possible for MinneHack to provide all our hackers with commemorative "MinneHack 2020" stickers! Make sure you come to the information booth in the back of the hall and pick one up!
